title: The Magic Roundabout - 5 Classsic Episodes + Intro (from 2-Disc
description:
These five episodes of the classic Magic Roundabout show are included on the 2-Disc Special Edition set of the 2005 UK film, which is only available on Region 2 so I wanted to make these files available to everybody (thank you multi-region player). Includes a short intro featurette.

Files:

Intro
Mr. Rusty Meets Zebedee (very first episode, and yeah I misspelled "Zebedee" on the file, I have a habit of typing "Zebadee" instead, sorry)
Camping
Perfume
Jumping Beans
Rocking Chair

Feel free to send reseed requests to me at sparky(at)theneitherworld.com and visit  my Magic Roundabout site at http://www.theneitherworld.com/tmr/ :)
